metadata.name: Woriax / Experiment
metadata.description:
He lives in Kiaraoluu, one of the KK sub-universes. A scientist who conducts experiments for the continuation of his generation.

Hand drawn. Remastered in Adobe Photoshop with a graphic tablet.
Illustrator: Kahraman Kılıç

Original size: 5906x8268 px
300dpi (50x70cm)
